cs.PF, cs.AR, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.SY 

This paper is likely to belong to the Performance Analysis and Optimization (cs.PF) sub-category as it focuses on hardware performance monitoring and pattern identification for high performance computing. Additionally, it may also fall under the sub-categories of Architecture (cs.AR) and Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) as it deals with hardware features and performance analysis in parallel computing systems. Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Systems and Control (cs.SY) are also possible sub-categories as the paper discusses the use of higher level tools and the identification of performance-limiting effects.
